Write a query to find city which had lowest percentage spend for gold card type 

select top 1 city,sum(amount) as total,1.0*100*sum(case when card_type='Gold' then amount else 0 end)/sum(amount) as Gold_contri from credit_card_transactions group by city having sum(case when card_type='Gold' then amount else 0 end)>0 order by Gold_contri
